==English==
===Verb===
'''[[pick up]] the [[phone]]'''
# To pick up the [[receiver]] of a [[telephone]].
# To answer an incoming telephone call.

====Synonyms====
*<!--universal synonyms-->[[pick the phone up]], [[pick up the telephone]]
*(''answer a call''): [[answer the phone]]

====Antonyms====
*[[hang up the phone]], [[hang the phone up]], [[hang up]]

====Translations====
*Portuguese: atender o telefone
*Spanish: descolgar el teléfono

